cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.DM, cs.CV, cs.NE 

The paper proposes a novel framework for multiple classifier generation and combination, which is a common topic in machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.LG, cs.AI). The proposed framework is based on fuzzy clustering, which is a technique commonly used in data mining and pattern recognition (cs.DM). The framework is also evaluated on 49 benchmarks, which are likely related to computer vision (cs.CV) and neural networks (cs.NE).
